{"type":null,"faqId":44832,"title":"能否将手机调整至单手模式？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.0826389in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">EMUI3.1特有“懒人模式”，手指在虚拟导航栏向左右滑动，即可实现单手模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 向左/右滑动导航栏，进入到单手操作界面；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 向相反方向滑动导航栏，退出单手操作界面；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">在“设置”中，点击“单手模式”，可以在“单手操作”界面下对“单手屏幕”和“单手键盘”进行设置。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"333","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409268000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":2,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"单手模式,调整","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}